org.hibernate.metamodel.model.domain.spi

Interface VersionSupport<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryVersionSupport, ByteVersionSupport, CalendarVersionSupport, InstantVersionSupport, IntegerVersionSupport, LocalDateTimeVersionSupport, LongVersionSupport, OffsetDateTimeVersionSupport, ShortVersionSupport, TimestampVersionSupport, ZonedDateTimeVersionSupport

    public interface VersionSupport<T>
    Additional contract for types which may be used to version (and optimistic lock) data.
